  "texts": [
    "When we reduced the number of vignettes in our final set, we maintained a criterion that all six vignettes had to have equal emotion intensity ratings, within and across emotion categories, as rated by the participants who also provided reappraisals.",
    "The selected vignettes also had at least 100 human reappraisals each, and the highest distinct emotion rated by participants matched the original intended emotion of each vignette (see Supplemental Information).",
    "To ensure that grammatical person did not affect the quality of the reappraisals, we converted those written in the first person to the second person, without altering the structure or meaning.",
    "We also edited the reappraisals for capitalization, punctuation, spelling, and general grammar errors.",
    "Generating GPT reappraisals."
  ],
